‚úÖ Step 6: Other Admin Features
Admin can also:
Once logged in, the Admin can perform various management tasks:
‚Ä¢	View Employees (Option 2)
View the list of employees currently added to the system.
‚Ä¢	Remove Employees (Option 3)
üîí Note: This option only works if at least one employee has been added.
‚Ä¢	Delete Food Items (Option 5)
üîí Note: This option only works if at least one food item has been added.
‚Ä¢	View Menu (Option 6)
